## Files

There are four R files.

The first one is about identifying for which identifiers there is data across all EHS data files: Merge_Data_EHS_Wellbeing3

The second one is the main analysis file: EHS_Wellbeing_Markdown12

The third one is a file for plotting some of the regression outcomes: plot_model_reduced

The four one is file for crossvalidation of the logistic regression models: crossvalidation_EHS_Wellbeing.R
